Dungeoneering | 24/7 VPS Hosted | Staff needed | Unique gaming experience | Vote4Reward | Forums [/url][/SIZE]
[size=5][i]Note: we are currently in [b]béta[/b] mode ! We currently are working on Squeal of Fortune[/i][/size]
[size=4]LiberationHD 718 is an unique gaming experience which is based on the needs of the common runescape player. We are an upcoming runescape private server with lots of potential, as our developping team is selected based on skills and motivation. With an amazing community, LiberationHD will succeed existing with a common goal: to become one of the biggest around.
Our experience will blow your mind with its amazing economy, bosses, minigames and much, much more. LiberationHD is a 718 revisioned server, which means we are a quiet modern sourced private server. With our daily Vote4Reward system, we never seem to stop amusing our players. Besides that, we are economy-based, which means we have a variety of donation possibilites. This means we are [b][i]NOT[/i][/b] a Pay2Win server !
